oracle.jdbc.aq.AQAgent

  • Packages that use AQAgent 
    Package Description
    oracle.jdbc.aq
    This package is an Oracle JDBC extension that provides interfaces to access the Advanced Queuing feature of Oracle for enterprise messaging applications.
